          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1724395905473-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion softens, peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 750ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[975ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1724395909711-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1724395909711-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1724395909711-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1724395909711-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1724395909711-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add your <strong>arborio rice </strong>and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains of rice in the oil</p><p>Add the <strong>stock</strong> a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 25-30 min or until all of the stock is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1724395913786-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1724395913786-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1724395913786-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1724395913786-x1000.jpg",
